com.informatica.mdm.api.sif

Class UserExitSifClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.informatica.mdm.api.sif.UserExitSifClient

  • public class UserExitSifClient
extends Object
    This is a special client class used exclusively to call SIF APIs from within a user exit context. The jdbc Connection from the user exit context is used throughout the SIF APIs called from this client in order to execute the APIs within the same transaction as the user exit.
    Author:
    echoi
